C:\Data\Nucleus_Dev\Vostok_ACU_A\source\XCategory\Common\all\SRCommon\SRTaskSequence\SRTaskSequence.c
      1          /**
      2           *  @file       SRTaskSequence.c
      3           *  @defgroup   CLASS_B
      4           *  @brief      Check for the correct execution sequence of Class B functions.
      5           *
      6           * @details     The SRTaskSequence module supports multiple function sequences.
      7           *
      8           *              The parameter files are used to define the function calls that make up each of
      9           *              the sequences. The function calls must occur in the same order that they are
     10           *              defined in the parameter files.
     11           *
     12           *              If a problem is encountered, the SRException contains data that can be used to
     13           *              diagnose the reason for the problem.
     14           *
     15           *              SREXCEPTION_SRTASKSEQ_INCOMPLETED occurs if the sequence is started or stopped in
     16           *              the middle of executing the sequence.
     17           *                  First Diagnostic Word: Hi byte = sequence id, Lo byte = sequence step number.
     18           *
     19           *              SREXCEPTION_SRTASKSEQ_WRONG_NUMBER occurs if a function was called out of order
     20           *              in the sequence.
     21           *                  First Diagnostic Word: Hi byte = sequence id, Lo byte = sequence step number.
     22           *                  Second Diagnostic Word: Hi byte = function id, Lo byte = expected function id.
     23           *
     24           *              SREXCEPTION_SRTASKSEQ_TIMEOUT occurs if the sequence took more than the alloted
     25           *              time to complete.
     26           *                  First Diagnostic Word: Hi byte = sequence id, Lo byte = sequence step number.
     27           *
     28           * @copyright   Copyright 2015-2017 Whirlpool Corporation.  All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL.
     29           */
